Package: wanna-build
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, perl5, libmldbm-perl
Recommends: exim | mail-transport-agent, cron, wget
Suggests: gnupg
Description: Database for Debian source packages needing to be compiled.
 wanna-build maintains a database of packages which need to be compiled.

Package: buildd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, perl5, sbuild (>= 0.49), dupload, cron, exim | mail-transport-agent
Description: Build daemon for automatically compiling Debian packages
 buildd is a build daemon which will compile Debian packages automatically.

